---
title: Roasted Pork Tenderloin and Shallot Gravy with Creamy Mash and Garlicky Broccoli
description: Shallot gravy is the star of this weeknight pork roast dinner, taking juicy pork tenderloin, creamy mash and garlicky broccoli to another level.
